        <abstract> 
<p>Sends copy of book containing measurements taken of individuals of different races during voyage of <hi rend="italic">Novara</hi> [Karl Heinrich von Scherzer, ed., <hi rend="italic">Reise der Fregatte "Novara", Anthropologischer Theil</hi> (1867)].</p> 
            <p>Asks for scientific advice concerning newly planned expedition.</p>
            <p>Says Carl Vogt plans to use data from book in lectures.</p>
        </abstract>
